eventOutputs.name: IND_TRANS
eventOutputs.comment: Sensors of transport unit have changed

eventOutputs.name: IND_PRESS
eventOutputs.comment: Sensors of press unit have changed

inputVars.name: TRANS_ADV1
inputVars.comment: Advance transport unit to position 1 (middle position), must be true until position MID is reachted

inputVars.name: TRANS_ADV2
inputVars.comment: Advance transport unit to position 2 (end position), must be true until position END is reachted

inputVars.name: TRANS_RET
inputVars.comment: Advance transport unit back to home position, must be true until position HOME is reachted

inputVars.name: PRESS_FWD
inputVars.comment: Advance press forward, must be true until position END is reachted

inputVars.name: PRESS_REV
inputVars.comment: Advance press backward, must be true until position HOME is reachted
